 and misunderstanding or mistranslation, particularly on those technical terms

44
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:30,000
 and ideas that the current AI may not have the context to understand.

45
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:34,000
 So please take it as reference only.

46
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:38,000
 This is actually part of our experience today.

47
