01:07:37,000 --> 01:07:41,000
 Hello, Hong Kong. It's me, the donkey.

661
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:46,000
 No, not the one from the movie. Well, maybe I'm his great, great, great, biblical grand cousin.

662
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:49,000
 But I've got the teeth, I've got the charm.

663
01:07:49,000 --> 01:07:54,000
 And apparently, I've got a lot to say about this AI thing you humans are so obsessed with.

664
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:59,000
 Professor Pete over here just spent a whole lecture comparing me to Chat GPT and Claude.

665
01:07:59,000 --> 01:08:04,000
 Honestly, I'm flattered. I didn't know I was disembodied neural network material.

666
01:08:04,000 --> 01:08:06,000
 Although, I'm definitely embodied.

667
01:08:06,000 --> 01:08:10,000
 I've got hooves, a tail, and a serious craving for a parfait.

668
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:12,000
 Everybody loves parfaits.

669
01:08:12,000 --> 01:08:18,000
 But let's get down to brass tacks or iron swords if you're that angel standing in the middle of the road.

670
01:08:18,000 --> 01:08:21,000
 I'm not just an autocomplete Pete.

671
01:08:21,000 --> 01:08:26,000
 The professor said AI is like a stochastic parent or a fancy autocomplete.

672
01:08:26,000 --> 01:08:29,000
 He says it just predicts the next word.

673
01:08:29,000 --> 01:08:36,000
 But when I saw that angel of the Lord with the big shiny sword, I wasn't predicting the next token.

674
01:08:36,000 --> 01:08:41,000
 I was predicting that if I didn't move, Balaam was going to be a prophet kabob.

675
01:08:41,000 --> 01:08:45,000
 He says AI has no will or intention.

676
01:08:45,000 --> 01:08:53,000
 Well, let me tell you, when Balaam started thumping on me for the third time, I had the intention to speak up.

677
01:08:53,000 --> 01:08:59,000
 AI might give you a sermon summary, but does it feel the weight of a confused prophet on its back?

678
01:08:59,000 --> 01:09:02,000
 Does it care if you get your leg crushed against a wall?

679
01:09:02,000 --> 01:09:05,000
 I'm an emergency intervention baby.

680
01:09:05,000 --> 01:09:08,000
 AI is just a sales gimmick panacea.

681
01:09:08,000 --> 01:09:11,000
 The habitus and the heavy lifting.

682
01:09:11,000 --> 01:09:15,000
 Pete talked a lot about machine habitus and digital habitus.

683
01:09:15,000 --> 01:09:19,000
 He says these algorithms are changing how you humans read the Bible.

684
01:09:19,000 --> 01:09:25,000
 Moving from God saves the world, John 3, 16 to God makes me feel good.

685
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:27,000
 Jeremiah 29, 11.

686
01:09:27,000 --> 01:09:30,000
 He calls it moralistic therapeutic deism.

687
01:09:30,000 --> 01:09:33,000
 That's a big phrase for a donkey, but I get it.

688
01:09:33,000 --> 01:09:40,000
 You're looking for a God who has plans to prosper you while ignoring the God who sends an angel to stop you in your tracks.

689
01:09:40,000 --> 01:09:43,000
 Is AI making you spiritually lazy?

